🚀 AI Resume Critiquer – Smart Resume Feedback with AI 🤖📃
I recently built an AI-powered Resume Critiquer using Streamlit and OpenAI API that helps users improve their resumes with instant, personalized feedback.
✨ Highlights
🔹 Upload resumes in PDF or TXT format
🔹 AI analyzes resume content and structure
🔹 Provides feedback on skills, experience, and clarity
🔹 Personalized suggestions based on the target job role
🔹 Simple and interactive UI built with Streamlit
🔹 Secure API key handling using dotenv
🛠️ Tech Stack
💻 Python
⚡ Streamlit
📚 PyPDF2
🤖 OpenAI API
🌱 dotenv
📚 What I Learned
✅ File handling and PDF text extraction
✅ Integrating AI APIs into web applications
✅ Writing effective prompts for better AI responses
✅ Building responsive and user-friendly apps
✅ Managing exceptions and improving application flow
🌟 Project Summary
This project was a great learning experience in combining AI with practical real-world applications. The Resume Critiquer helps users receive structured and actionable resume feedback within seconds, making resume improvement faster and smarter. It also strengthened my understanding of API integration, prompt engineering, and interactive web app development using Python. Looking forward to adding more features like ATS score analysis, keyword optimization, and downloadable reports in future updates.
